name: Stable BTD6
description:
This model was trained on all the monkeys from the game BTD6 by Ninja Kiwi.

Use prompt: 'btdmnky' to get a monkey. You can use the categories in the game to generate a monkey based on that category, such as putting "btdmnky magic" will generate a monkey based on the magic monkeys in-game. You can use:

  • primary
  • military
  • magic
  • support (results won't be great)
  • hero

This model can generate monkeys with specific characters or creatures in mind. Goblins work pretty well! Other characters can make the image quality lower, as seen with the harry potter monkey in the examples.
